quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  70,36,Quod keeping those est disbelieved ligatus vos
  70,37,To the statim to sinister they flee
  70,38,Quam potuit any de them expect iniit blissful Paradise
  70,39,Nunquam; nos created them they know ex quod
  70,40,Ego solemnly juravit Dominus de easts wests; nos est able
  70,41,to substitute bene people tuus locus; nos nunquam defeated
  70,42,Ergo let them blunder play they meet feria awaiting them
  70,43,Ut est feria they advenit graves in ut hurry prout si herded (sacrificial) altare
  70,44,Cum their eyes subdued shame cover them. Ut est feria awaiting them